text: Nedjeljko Mihanović (; 16 February 1930 – 27 January 2022) was a Croatian politician. He was Speaker of the Croatian Parliament from 1994 to 1995. He retired in 2000. He died on 27 January 2022, at the age of 91. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Croatian politicians
title: Nedjeljko Mihanović
